title.narrative: Support to the increase of levels of productivity and competitiveness in Zambia’s private sector- Fees and Expenses for Supplier

description.narrative: This activity (Support to the increase of levels of productivity and competitiveness in Zambia’s private sector- Fees and Expenses for Supplier) is a component of Private Enterprise Programme in Zambia reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Not for profit organisation' and a budget of £13,761,126. This component benefits Zambia, and works in the following sector(s): Formal sector financial intermediaries, Business Policy and Administration, Small and medium-sized enterprises (SME) development. , with the following implementing partners: DAI Europe. The start date is 02-01-2012 and the end date is 30-06-2020.
